Text.string: You think I'm scared of the Ursa Corps?!
Always wanted to kill an Ursa!
Hey, old man, don't run from me!
Let's go a round WITHOUT those gadgets!
I'll show you how a real man fights, blondie!
Let's see what you got, Siren!
Yes! Time to frag a Siren!
Kill the Siren, get a bonus!
Oh, you brought me a snack!
Show me what you're made of!
I think you suck! Prove me wrong.
Did you want a few pointers?
You're not fit to shine my boots!
Don't you dare run from me!
Get back here and fight me!
I'm gonna be the last thing you see!
Let me introduce you to my gun!
Gonna shove this gun down your throat!
After I kill ya, I'm going out for STEAK!
Why can't I just shoot forever?
Serving up a steaming heap of death!
Just die so I can get my bonus!
This is my hill to die on!
Need some cover! Help me out!
Damn it! Give me some cover!
Just open up on this jagoff!
Moving to assist. Don't get used to it!
I gotcha! Now let's get PAID!
Watch your six! Or three, or nine, or... Whatever! Clocks suck, you're still gonna die!
Hey, get outta there! Heh heh heh.
Always knew I'd blow up someday!
I'm out of control! Like, in a bad way!
This looks like a good spot!
I never mastered the pan flute!
That pack is comin' in hot!
Called it! Didn't I call it?
I ain't your damn medic. Get good.
Okay, but this is the last time!
Get this friggin' thing offa me!
Don't eat me, don't EAT ME!
That beast is on frickin' ROIDS!
How'd you know I hate rakks?!
I don't get paid enough for this!
Yeah yeah, we got mechs too!
One of them's gotta be real!
Now I don't know WHO to kill!
Get that crap off my battlefield!
I gotta deal with THIS now?
Makin' me work for it, huh?
That's right! Cower behind your walls!
I can wait. I got time!
Let that be a lesson to you!
Don't go out like that dumbass!
MAL's gonna hand out bonuses for this!
You know how much your head's worth?
Told ya our tech was better!
I don't even need this thing!
I'll see you in hell! Bring guac...
I was kind of... a monster anyway...
You call that a kill streak?
Man, y'all are bad at this!
Well, shoot. Looks like you CAN fight.
Get up and fight RIGHT NOW!
I ain't goin' out like them!
I can still take you, Vaulter!
Whatever. Try and take ME down!
Wanna learn a thing or two?
Am I supposed to fight alone?
I can't win this war by myself!
And I thought you could hang!
This was over before it started!
Came in thinkin' you big and bad.
Come back when you got skills!
I got all the time in the world!
Here I thought you'd be a challenge.
Thought you guys might miss the fun!
You guys ready to earn your bonus?
Left me hanging for a sec there!
Where the hell have you scrubs been?
MAL, where the hell are you?
We're dyin' here! Need a shield!
You're gonna be a sorry sight when I'm through with you!
Stop and let me kill you already!
Hey, Vaulter! You suck at this!
Come at me when you've got the skills!
I'm not stickin' around for this!
This wasn't in the job description!
Screw you, Vaulter! I'm outta here!
Exit stage right! Or -- or left! Whatever!
Go on, test me! I dare ya!
Try me and see what happens!
I'm pretty sure you're screwed! Ha!
I ain't too worried about it.
Gah... This one's lost its edge!
Don't let me die, damn it!
